  "title": "A star-shaped UFO moving in circles over Curitiba [2002]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/11/a-star-shaped-ufo-moving-in-circles-over-curitiba-2002/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-jn",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>AUG 8th, 2002</strong>. 10:48 pm. Duration: 25 seconds. In the Batel neighborhood of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a university professor, using binoculars, spotted an unidentified red star-shaped flying object, moving in circles, flying at an altitude of approximately 5,000ft and heading West from the East. The sighting of the unidentified flying object was carried out under conditions of visibility described as &#8220;good&#8221;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.625. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário relata avistamento de ovni no bairro de Batel, em Curitiba, Paraná&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>AUG 8th, 2002. 10:48 pm. Duration: 25 seconds. In the Batel neighborhood of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a university professor, using binoculars, spotted an unidentified red star-shaped flying object, moving in circles, flying at an altitude of approximately 5,000ft and heading West from the East. The sighting of the unidentified flying object was carried out [&hellip;]</p>\n",
